{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "08b14c26-6cd3-489f-9146-641e8f3fa67e",
    "name": "Magic Class Session 1 07 Glow Stone",
    "sceneId": "981d126b-abc7-430a-abb4-e912340c59e6",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "f7063fdf-76c1-4f02-8458-d372923dfdad",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "f7a1373b-46d1-4690-a486-49b3709ec3a6",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "65228698-904b-4d4d-9d61-c72c2fab5452",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today, we will be working at the rune tables where you will get to create your very first runestone! Think of it as a personalized magic item that only works for you. ",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "b0a6f275-68d2-42f2-a99a-3a2b0604fb8b",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "I will give all of you some special clay taken from the shores of Cor Magicis. It has many different magical properties, but today we are going to use its capacity as a storage for Mojo and a focus for runes.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "46132b8c-091e-4e26-a4b9-a7fcfb2e24a8",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "First you will shape the clay into a sphere. Poke your thumb into the center of the sphere and then whisper your name into it. You must properly introduce yourself to the clay to make the magic bind to your Will... er... Moxie.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "88988d0a-26dc-49b1-9ea3-19116594f0ff",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Then we shall flatten out the sphere into a circular dome and precisely inscribe the runes for \"Self\" and \"Light\" onto it. At the same time, you should be intoning the mantra, Fiat Lux, repeatedly as you shape the rune stone.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "f262ba6e-0c01-435c-8e95-06591d628f6c",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Finally, we will be firing the runestones in a specially designed kiln with magical flames to bake in the spell, the shape, and the magic.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "id": "5443c7b4-e979-4cd1-a01d-56db4043f2c1",
                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                    "skill": "Magic",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "0ba9006c-7231-48fe-9886-518aa6bd85e8",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions before we proceed?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "4d5a38e2-8a1b-4a74-83e6-8a8ae7b6fe88",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "6592219c-beca-4c8d-bf84-2e7a3d8ededb",
                            "text": "Ask How to Use the Runestone",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "c960320e-d82e-426a-a1cf-5d43b10cc1ac",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "How do we use a runestone once we make it?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "cd14bd2a-ae82-4983-81fc-70bd336607e1",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Each runestone will have its own mantra - a small phrase unique to the type of spell you wish to invoke. In the case of the Glow spell, we use the phrase <i>Fiat Lux</i> which roughly translates to \"Let the Light be done.\"",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "eaa99484-6cff-49de-a907-356a1a1dcc01",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "To cast the Glow spell, simply rub your finger over the runes as you sub-vocalize \"Fiat Lux.\"",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "60a1ec60-0d1a-4a5a-9ad2-4e6e267161cf",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "3acba60f-635a-4d3f-aa8b-a4d8c55026b6",
                            "text": "Ask About the Shape of the Rune Stone",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "064ab682-b9a0-400c-bcff-06c78976bc96",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Why a round shape? Couldn't it be shaped like a square or shaped like the rune?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3802d120-8cfe-483d-a1d5-d5413d0e1df1",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "The reason we are shaping this runestone into a rounded disk is because this is a personal spell to be used upon yourself. It should fit comfortably in your hand as you invoke the spell.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7a1af296-5b1f-4a74-b105-3dfd6903b960",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "In a later class, we will be constructing a runestone that is designed to be placed upon the ground and triggered when something comes near it. Such rune stones are rectangular shaped.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d35ea164-26ae-43de-838a-e45bc4bc8f76",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "After all, Form follows Function, at least in magical terms.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "245d89d6-b07f-4161-8894-147cd5bc368d",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "c027f89e-af52-414d-a6e9-8c40f9c070b6",
                            "text": "Ask About Introducing Yourself to the Clay",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "747e2aca-f7b7-4049-be2f-5dfc1c819262",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "What do you mean by introducing yourself to a ball of clay? \"Hello, clay, I'm Shawn O'Conner, I'm pleased to meet you.\" ",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ebb79b9f-611a-48be-8eaf-0925ea7aad2c",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Courtesy is always in order, although perhaps a polite attitude is more important than a sarcastic one...",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "c26e7f46-2953-4284-9a97-fd7c6072009b",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "In this case, though, by saying your name to the center of the clay, you are binding the magic in the clay to do your bidding. Names are very powerful tools in magic.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "999e84dd-77cc-471b-b656-2becdb52d04e",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "31",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "6afd0995-4db7-44ce-98bc-5f6e406a1bdc",
                            "text": "Say Nothing",
                            "nodes": [],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                    "id": "5e15af2b-5c9f-433e-9503-6b1058dccd26",
                    "name": "Here we Glow!",
                    "notify": true,
                    "description": "Today we made a 'Glow for It' runestone that casts a magical light around me that only I can see. It should help whenever I'm exploring dark places.\n\nAll I have to do is rub the stone and say the words, 'Fiat Lux.' Seems simple enough."
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "a33f8826-5d54-4285-b1e0-5afa8419d590",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Then let us begin the construction of the Glow runestone...",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeInventory",
                    "id": "49c9422b-6268-4474-86bb-95d5ecd1ef12",
                    "propId": "7ef8bf45-b578-4ccf-b111-4cd7318e42a9",
